item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Trey D - 1999 album (songs featuring NSYNC and Backstreet Boys)
item.description:
Hello, does anyone happen to own a copy of Trey D’s 1999 album released under Edel Records. He was a rapper mostly known for his ties with Backstreet Boys and NSYNC. The album is no where to be found on the internet in good quality. There were even 2 duets on the album with JC Chasez of NSYNC and Kevin Richardson of BSB.
Really hope someone can help! At least for the 2 duets.
Link of the album: https://www.allmusic.com/album/release/trey-d-mr0000113397
